ious media outlets for publication. You will receive a portion of the proceeds of any sales received by Bravo Your City for any such publication in accordance with the User Payment Terms (</span><span class="c0 c8 c11"><a class="c14" href="http://www.bravoyourcity.com/static/payments">http://www.bravoyourcity.com/static/payments</a></span><span class="c0">)</span><span class="c0">. Once your User Content has been distributed to a local media outlet, you may not remove the User Content from the Service or restrict Bravo Your City or its licensees from further distributing that User Content in any way. For the avoidance of doubt, nothing in this Section restricts your ability to distribute User Content you provide to the Service.</span></p><ol class="c2" start="6"><li class="c10 c3"><span class="c0 c5 c8">Disclaimer of Representation</span></li></ol><p class="c4"><span class="c0">You acknowledge and agree that Bravo Your City has no obligation to distribute, sell, market, or promote any User Content you provide to the Service in any form or through any media channel, and that any such distribution or promotion shall be at the sole discretion of Bravo Your City. </span><span class="c0">Nothing in this Agreement shall be construed as created any agent or representative relationship </span><span class="c0">between you and Bravo Your City.</span></p><p class="c4 c9"><span class="c0"></span></p><ol class="c2" start="7"><li class="c10 c3"><span class="c0 c5 c8">Mobile Softwar</span><span class="c0 c5 c8">e </span></li></ol><ol class="c7" start="1"><li class="c1"><span class="c0 c5">Mobile Software</span><span class="c0">. &nbsp;We may make available software to access the Service via a mobile device (&ldquo;Mobile Software&rdquo;). &nbsp;To use the Mobile Software you must have a mobile device that is compatible with the Mobile Service. &nbsp;Bravo Your City does not warrant that the Mobile Software will be compatible with your mobile device. &nbsp;Bravo Your City hereby gr